    "subject": "Refactor javadoc comments in EchoXML",
    "body": "This commit refactors the javadoc comments in the EchoXML class to improve readability and clarity. Specifically, it removes unnecessary comments and renames 'Other limitations' to 'Known limitations'. The changes do not affect the functionality of the class, which remains the same."
}

